    "body": "This behavior is intended, you can find more about it at:\nhttp://electron.atom.io/docs/v0.36.0/api/remote/#passing-callbacks-to-the-main-process\n\nAnd unfortunately there is no way to fix this for now, the download API exposed by Chromium is synchronous, unless we did a big refactor of related Chromium code, we have to live with it.\n"
